    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <span class="stat-label">Based in</span>
        <span class="stat-value">Chennai, India</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="stat-label">Focus</span>
        <span class="stat-value">Design & Dev</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="stat-label">Status</span>
