      <div class="resume-org">University or Institution</div>
      <p class="resume-desc">Field of study. Any honours, thesis work, or notable achievements.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-entry-top">
        <span class="resume-role">Design & Tools</span>
      </div>
      <p class="resume-desc" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Figma, Illustrator, Photoshop, Framer — or whatever tools you use. List yours here.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-entry">
      <div class="resume-entry-top">
        <span class="resume-role">Development</span>
      </div>
      <p class="resume-desc" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">HTML / CSS / JS, React, Python, or whatever stack you work in. Make it yours.</p>
    </div>
